Create a new branch from master eg : security

Push branch and spin up the pantheon environment with db from live .
on new branch run commands :
----------------------------------
git pull git://github.com/pantheon-systems/drops-8.git master    // pull master branch updates from pantheon
git push origin security    // push to new branch and run updates through terminal on that branch if any
----------------------------------

Test all to be fine on new enviornment and if all fine merge the new branch in maser and push to all sites. 
Eg : 
git checkout master
git merge security master
git push origin master

Reference : http://helpdesk.getpantheon.com/customer/portal/articles/361248-core-updates
